<p>I finished my B.S. in Informatics while abroad, and completed an anthropological analysis of this subculture as a final project.</p>

<p>You can read the paper <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1deRn1GY3A-YWmuzv-tacOQqQodWIQqQWJ9PnZidKvxg/edit?usp=sharing">here.</a></p>

